data.description: Nestled in a quiet neighborhood is this cute 4-bedroom split level home on a large lot. Come take a look at the updated kitchen, new flooring throughout, all led lighting, open concept, new bathrooms (with heated fog free mirrors), RV parking, back deck, & spacious backyard. Attached garage is a great place to store all of your toys or use for hobbies. All appliances stay!! Contractor is just finishing up a few more items. House feels like new! Call today to take a look.
